He said: ‘I’d love to use the line, it’s a tough job, but somebody has to do it, but I’d be lying as it probably is the best job in the world.

‘I’ve been a fitness trainer since 1999 and never realised when I started out that my diploma in fitness training and sports therapy would lead to anything like this.

‘The contestants are all stunning and very glamorous, but they range in fitness from fairly unfit to spectacularly fit.

‘I had to supervise the tests and mark them and a few girls literally collapsed with exhaustion afterwards.

